snippet.title: MediEvil (PS1) PS5 Gameplay (PS Plus Premium)
snippet.description:
Hi, welcome to 4 Gamers Gaming! In todays video we are playing MediEvil (PS1) PS5 Gameplay (PS Plus Premium)! Please like, comment, and subscribe! #Medievil #PS5 #psplus #Gaming

Link to our Twitter: https://twitter.com/4GamersGaming1

Link to our Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/4gamersgamingyt/

Link to our Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/4gamersgamingyt

Hi, we are the 4 Gamers Gaming. We are 4 siblings gaming together!  Our channel's videos are of us playing various genres of video games on PS2, PS4, PS5, Wii U, Wii, and Nintendo Switch. Player 1 is Redsmvp, Player 2 is BlueFender, Player 3 is PokeColor8, Player 4 is Rainboily10. We play a lot of 4-Player Co-Op games, and also a lot of single player games as well! Some of our most common games are Sackboy: A Big Adventure, Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl, Fall Guys, and Fortnite. But we also post fun new releases and retro games! If you like our videos, please like and subscribe to our channel. We strive to put out the best content we can and have it full of fun and positivity! Thanks for watching!

4 Gamers Gaming
